ai-kv7.3:1.1_0: It’s not even analyzed of intentions.
ai-kv7.3:1.3_0: Doesn’t there come together with thoughts associated with the objects of the mind? Though they have a single sense of urgency, and there is one object,
ai-kv7.3:1.5_0: “There are states that are present in the sense of urgency, and eighteen objects—born as a single object, stilling to the cessation of the object.
ai-kv7.3:1.6_0: “There is no principle because of intention.”
ai-kv7.3:2.4_0: “There is an intentional emission of semen.”
ai-kv7.3:2.16_0: and lack of conscience and prudence,
ai-kv7.3:2.18_0: and come with a thousand conscience and prudence, he surely said to him,
ai-kv7.3:3.7_0: If you’re not free of greed, desire, fondness, thirst, passion, and craving for feeling ...
ai-kv7.3:3.18_0: and without prudent he gave him permission.
ai-kv7.3:4.1_0: It’s not even analyzed of intentions.
ai-kv7.3:5.2_0: if he has not a non-self;
ai-kv7.3:5.3_0: Then, knowing the lowest of knowledge,
ai-kv7.3:6.3_0: Therefore there is an exterminator as Dhamma.
ai-kv7.3:7.1_0: It’s not even analyzed of intentions.
ai-kv7.3:7.4_0: “Take a mendicant who reveals another person’s thoughts.’
ai-kv7.3:7.5_0: ‘This is what you’re thinking, such is your thought.’”
ai-kv7.3:7.8_0: Therefore there is an exterminator as Dhamma.
ai-kv7.3:7.9_0: The discussion on mental objects is finished.
